0.jpg 629w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16133146/delta-cycle-x-mount-pro-steerer-cap-mount-2.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16133146/delta-cycle-x-mount-pro-steerer-cap-mount-2-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16133146/delta-cycle-x-mount-pro-steerer-cap-mount-2-800x534.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16133146/delta-cycle-x-mount-pro-steerer-cap-mount-2-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16133146/delta-cycle-x-mount-pro-steerer-cap-mount-2-768x513.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16133146/delta-cycle-x-mount-pro-steerer-cap-mount-2-696x465.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16133146/delta-cycle-x-mount-pro-steerer-cap-mount-2-1068x713.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16133146/delta-cycle-x-mount-pro-steerer-cap-mount-2-629x420.jpg 629w\"></a></p><p>It has a slight rise angle, so won’t work for “comfort” stems that have an extreme angle. But for most normal stems with 12º or less, it should fit fine, especially if you have another spacer between it and the top of the stem.</p><p>I found that these, and the XL Holders below, captured the phones easily and held them well enough for commuting and running errands. I wouldn’t use them for more aggressive road, gravel, or mountain biking…but for casual riding, they worked great and I applaud the well-thought-out feature set and universal fit.</p><h3>Delta Smartphone Holder XL</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16075627/delta-cycles-deluxe-phone-holder-review-01.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16075627/delta-cycles-deluxe-phone-holder-review-01.jpg\" alt=\"delta smartphone holder xl handlebar mounted phone case\" width=\"1200\" height=\"799\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16075627/delta-cycles-deluxe-phone-holder-review-01.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16075627/delta-cycles-deluxe-phone-holder-review-01.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16075627/delta-cycles-deluxe-phone-holder-review-01-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16075627/delta-cycles-deluxe-phone-holder-review-01-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16075627/delta-cycles-deluxe-phone-holder-review-01-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16075627/delta-cycles-deluxe-phone-holder-review-01-768x511.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16075627/delta-cycles-deluxe-phone-holder-review-01-696x463.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16075627/delta-cycles-deluxe-phone-holder-review-01-1068x711.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16075627/delta-cycles-deluxe-phone-holder-review-01-631x420.jpg 631w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16075627/delta-cycles-deluxe-phone-holder-review-01.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16075627/delta-cycles-deluxe-phone-holder-review-01-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16075627/delta-cycles-deluxe-phone-holder-review-01-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16075627/delta-cycles-deluxe-phone-holder-review-01-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16075627/delta-cycles-deluxe-phone-holder-review-01-768x511.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16075627/delta-cycles-deluxe-phone-holder-review-01-696x463.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16075627/delta-cycles-deluxe-phone-holder-review-01-1068x711.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16075627/delta-cycles-deluxe-phone-holder-review-01-631x420.jpg 631w\"></a></p><p>Available in normal and XL, these options are great for cruisers and other bicycles with bigger sweeping handlebars. Or older bikes with really narrow diameter handlebars. As long as you don’t have much else mounted to your bars…the XL is big, and takes up a lot of real estate.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16075644/delta-cycles-deluxe-phone-holder-review-02.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/16075644/delta-cycles-deluxe-phone-holder-review-02.jpg\" alt=\"delta smartphone holder xl handlebar mounted phone case\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngc